name: Lost#5 2°61’41”S//60°40’35"W
description:
The arrival

I'm very tired, I've been walking for hours looking for that place of the song.
Finally! I did it! ecstasy invade me. I find it difficult to put my happiness into words, this strange place must be its core, I see life sprouting from the ground and covering it with bright colors. I'm very close to that place where she wouldn't let me in, maybe I gained her trust in some way. She's finally being nice to me.
I am in a lot of pain and can barely move around the place. Fatigue and hunger strike again.
Today I remembered the beautiful things of my distant home, the warmth of mine, the wonderful flavors that I long for so much, I will stay here and try to rest.
